<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.10.1">
<l>kaṇṇārk kaṭaṟcū ḻilaṅkaik kiṟaivantaṉ</l>
<l>tiṇṇā kampiḷak ka<supplied>c</supplied>caram celavuyttāy</l>
<l>viṇṇōr toḻumvēṅ kaṭamā malaimēya</l>
<l>vaṇṇā vaṭiyē ṉiṭaraik kaḷaiyāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who shot an arrow so [it] went to split the strong chest</l>
<l>Of the lord of Lanka, encircled by the space-filled sea,</l>
<l>Lord who dwells on the great Vēṅkaṭa Mountain where celestials worship;</l>
<l>I am your servant; cast off [my] pain!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
